      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  Of <persName key="pers:Vīraseṇaka">Vīraseṇaka</persName>,
	  a chief householder and upright merchant, the meritorious
	  gift of a chetiyaghara, presented for the welfare and
	  happiness of all.
	</p>
